# Spike Template

Use this template for time-boxed exploration when a plan has high uncertainty.

---

## When to Use

Create a spike when:
- A plan has "Uncertainty: High" in metadata
- A review identifies unvalidated critical assumptions
- Implementation approach is unclear
- External dependency behavior is unknown
- Performance characteristics need validation

